{"surah":{"number":55,"name":"الرحمن","englishName":"Ar-Rahman","englishTranslation":"The Beneficent","ayahCount":78},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:18.048Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"The Most Merciful","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنُ","english":"The Most Gracious","translit":"al-raḥmānu","root":"رحم"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"Taught the Qur'an,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَلَّمَ","english":"He taught","translit":"ʿallama","root":"علم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْقُرْءَانَ","english":"the Quran","translit":"l-qur'āna","root":"قرأ"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"Created man,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"خَلَقَ","english":"He created","translit":"khalaqa","root":"خلق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ","english":"[the] man","translit":"l-insāna","root":"أنس"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"[And] taught him eloquence.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَلَّمَهُ","english":"He taught him","translit":"ʿallamahu","root":"علم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْبَيَانَ","english":"[the] speech","translit":"l-bayāna","root":"بين"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"The sun and the moon [move] by precise calculation,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلشَّمْسُ","english":"The sun","translit":"al-shamsu","root":"شمس"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَٱلْقَمَرُ","english":"and the moon","translit":"wal-qamaru","root":"قمر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِحُسْبَانٍۢ","english":"by (precise) calculation","translit":"biḥus'bānin","root":"حسب"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"And the stars and trees prostrate.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّجْمُ","english":"And the stars","translit":"wal-najmu","root":"نجم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَٱلشَّجَرُ","english":"and the trees","translit":"wal-shajaru","root":"شجر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَسْجُدَانِ","english":"both prostrate","translit":"yasjudāni","root":"سجد"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"And the heaven He raised and imposed the balance","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءَ","english":"And the heaven","translit":"wal-samāa","root":"سمو"},{"position":2,"arabic":"رَفَعَهَا","english":"He raised it","translit":"rafaʿahā","root":"رفع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَوَضَعَ","english":"and He has set up","translit":"wawaḍaʿa","root":"وضع"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمِيزَانَ","english":"the balance","translit":"l-mīzāna","root":"وزن"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"That you not transgress within the balance.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَلَّا","english":"That not","translit":"allā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَطْغَوْا۟","english":"you may transgress","translit":"taṭghaw","root":"طغي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمِيزَانِ","english":"the balance","translit":"l-mīzāni","root":"وزن"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"And establish weight in justice and do not make deficient the balance.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَقِيمُوا۟","english":"And establish","translit":"wa-aqīmū","root":"قوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْوَزْنَ","english":"the weight","translit":"l-wazna","root":"وزن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِٱلْقِسْطِ","english":"in justice","translit":"bil-qis'ṭi","root":"قسط"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and (do) not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تُخْسِرُوا۟","english":"make deficient","translit":"tukh'sirū","root":"خسر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْمِيزَانَ","english":"the balance","translit":"l-mīzāna","root":"وزن"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"And the earth He laid [out] for the creatures.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ","english":"And the earth","translit":"wal-arḍa","root":"أرض"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَضَعَهَا","english":"He laid it","translit":"waḍaʿahā","root":"وضع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِلْأَنَامِ","english":"for the creatures","translit":"lil'anāmi","root":"أنم"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"Therein is fruit and palm trees having sheaths [of dates]","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"Therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَـٰكِهَةٌۭ","english":"(is) fruit","translit":"fākihatun","root":"فكه"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّخْلُ","english":"and date-palms","translit":"wal-nakhlu","root":"نخل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذَاتُ","english":"having","translit":"dhātu","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْأَكْمَامِ","english":"sheaths","translit":"l-akmāmi","root":"كمم"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"And grain having husks and scented plants.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلْحَبُّ","english":"And the grain","translit":"wal-ḥabu","root":"حبب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ذُو","english":"having","translit":"dhū","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْعَصْفِ","english":"husk","translit":"l-ʿaṣfi","root":"عصف"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱلرَّيْحَانُ","english":"and scented plants","translit":"wal-rayḥānu","root":"روح"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"He created man from clay like [that of] pottery.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"خَلَقَ","english":"He created","translit":"khalaqa","root":"خلق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ","english":"the man","translit":"l-insāna","root":"أنس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"صَلْصَـٰلٍۢ","english":"clay","translit":"ṣalṣālin","root":"صلصل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"كَٱلْفَخَّارِ","english":"like the pottery","translit":"kal-fakhāri","root":"فخر"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"And He created the jinn from a smokeless flame of fire.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَخَلَقَ","english":"And He created","translit":"wakhalaqa","root":"خلق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجَآنَّ","english":"the jinn","translit":"l-jāna","root":"جنن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَّارِجٍۢ","english":"a smokeless flame","translit":"mārijin","root":"مرج"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"نَّارٍۢ","english":"fire","translit":"nārin","root":"نور"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"[He is] Lord of the two sunrises and Lord of the two sunsets.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"رَبُّ","english":"Lord","translit":"rabbu","root":"ربب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمَشْرِقَيْنِ","english":"(of) the two Easts","translit":"l-mashriqayni","root":"شرق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَرَبُّ","english":"and Lord","translit":"warabbu","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمَغْرِبَيْنِ","english":"(of) the two Wests","translit":"l-maghribayni","root":"غرب"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"He released the two seas, meeting [side by side];","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَرَجَ","english":"He released","translit":"maraja","root":"مرج"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْبَحْرَيْنِ","english":"the two seas","translit":"l-baḥrayni","root":"بحر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَلْتَقِيَانِ","english":"meeting","translit":"yaltaqiyāni","root":"لقي"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"Between them is a barrier [so] neither of them transgresses.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"بَيْنَهُمَا","english":"Between both of them","translit":"baynahumā","root":"بين"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بَرْزَخٌۭ","english":"(is) a barrier","translit":"barzakhun","root":"برزخ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَّا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَبْغِيَانِ","english":"they transgress","translit":"yabghiyāni","root":"بغي"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"From both of them emerge pearl and coral.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَخْرُجُ","english":"Come forth","translit":"yakhruju","root":"خرج"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِنْهُمَا","english":"from both of them","translit":"min'humā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللُّؤْلُؤُ","english":"the pearl","translit":"l-lu'lu-u","root":"لؤلؤ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱلْمَرْجَانُ","english":"and the coral","translit":"wal-marjānu","root":"مرج"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"And to Him belong the ships [with sails] elevated in the sea like mountains.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَهُ","english":"And for Him","translit":"walahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجَوَارِ","english":"(are) the ships","translit":"l-jawāri","root":"جري"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمُنشَـَٔاتُ","english":"elevated","translit":"l-munshaātu","root":"نشأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْبَحْرِ","english":"the sea","translit":"l-baḥri","root":"بحر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كَٱلْأَعْلَـٰمِ","english":"like mountains","translit":"kal-aʿlāmi","root":"علم"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"Everyone upon the earth will perish,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كُلُّ","english":"Everyone","translit":"kullu","root":"كلل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَنْ","english":"who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْهَا","english":"(is) on it","translit":"ʿalayhā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَانٍۢ","english":"(will) perish","translit":"fānin","root":"فني"}]},{"number":27,"translation":"And there will remain the Face of your Lord, Owner of Majesty and Honor.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيَبْقَىٰ","english":"But will remain","translit":"wayabqā","root":"بقي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَجْهُ","english":"(the) Face","translit":"wajhu","root":"وجه"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذُو","english":"(the) Owner","translit":"dhū","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْجَلَـٰلِ","english":"(of) Majesty","translit":"l-jalāli","root":"جلل"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱلْإِكْرَامِ","english":"and Honor","translit":"wal-ik'rāmi","root":"كرم"}]},{"number":28,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":29,"translation":"Whoever is within the heavens and earth asks Him; every day He is bringing about a matter.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَسْـَٔلُهُۥ","english":"Asks Him","translit":"yasaluhu","root":"سأل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَن","english":"whoever","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(is) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","english":"the heavens","translit":"l-samāwāti","root":"سمو"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ ۚ","english":"and the earth","translit":"wal-arḍi","root":"أرض"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كُلَّ","english":"Every","translit":"kulla","root":"كلل","audio":"wbw/055_029_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"يَوْمٍ","english":"day","translit":"yawmin","root":"يوم","audio":"wbw/055_029_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"He","translit":"huwa","root":"","audio":"wbw/055_029_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(is) in","translit":"fī","root":"","audio":"wbw/055_029_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"شَأْنٍۢ","english":"a matter","translit":"shanin","root":"شأن","audio":"wbw/055_029_011.mp3"}]},{"number":30,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":31,"translation":"We will attend to you, O prominent beings.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"سَنَفْرُغُ","english":"Soon We will attend","translit":"sanafrughu","root":"فرغ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"to you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَيُّهَ","english":"O you","translit":"ayyuha","root":"أيي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلثَّقَلَانِ","english":"two classes","translit":"l-thaqalāni","root":"ثقل"}]},{"number":32,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":33,"translation":"O company of jinn and mankind, if you are able to pass beyond the regions of the heavens and the earth, then pass. You will not pass except by authority [from Allah].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰمَعْشَرَ","english":"O assembly","translit":"yāmaʿshara","root":"عشر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجِنِّ","english":"(of) the jinn","translit":"l-jini","root":"جنن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱلْإِنسِ","english":"and the men","translit":"wal-insi","root":"أنس"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِنِ","english":"If","translit":"ini","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱسْتَطَعْتُمْ","english":"you are able","translit":"is'taṭaʿtum","root":"طوع"},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَن","english":"to","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"تَنفُذُوا۟","english":"pass beyond","translit":"tanfudhū","root":"نفذ"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مِنْ","english":"[of]","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"أَقْطَارِ","english":"(the) regions","translit":"aqṭāri","root":"قطر"},{"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","english":"(of) the heavens","translit":"l-samāwāti","root":"سمو"},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","english":"and the earth","translit":"wal-arḍi","root":"أرض"},{"position":12,"arabic":"فَٱنفُذُوا۟ ۚ","english":"then pass","translit":"fa-unfudhū","root":"نفذ"},{"position":13,"arabic":"لَا","english":"Not","translit":"lā","root":"","audio":"wbw/055_033_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"تَنفُذُونَ","english":"you (can) pass","translit":"tanfudhūna","root":"نفذ","audio":"wbw/055_033_015.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":"","audio":"wbw/055_033_016.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"بِسُلْطَـٰنٍۢ","english":"by authority","translit":"bisul'ṭānin","root":"سلط","audio":"wbw/055_033_017.mp3"}]},{"number":34,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":35,"translation":"There will be sent upon you a flame of fire and smoke, and you will not defend yourselves.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يُرْسَلُ","english":"Will be sent","translit":"yur'salu","root":"رسل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمَا","english":"against both of you","translit":"ʿalaykumā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"شُوَاظٌۭ","english":"a flame","translit":"shuwāẓun","root":"شوظ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"نَّارٍۢ","english":"fire","translit":"nārin","root":"نور"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَنُحَاسٌۭ","english":"and smoke","translit":"wanuḥāsun","root":"نحس"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَلَا","english":"and not","translit":"falā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"تَنتَصِرَانِ","english":"you will (be able to) defend yourselves","translit":"tantaṣirāni","root":"نصر"}]},{"number":36,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":37,"translation":"And when the heaven is split open and becomes rose-colored like oil -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِذَا","english":"Then when","translit":"fa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱنشَقَّتِ","english":"is split","translit":"inshaqqati","root":"شقق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءُ","english":"the heaven","translit":"l-samāu","root":"سمو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَكَانَتْ","english":"and it becomes","translit":"fakānat","root":"كون"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَرْدَةًۭ","english":"rose-colored","translit":"wardatan","root":"ورد"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كَٱلدِّهَانِ","english":"like murky oil","translit":"kal-dihāni","root":"دهن"}]},{"number":38,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny? -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":39,"translation":"Then on that Day none will be asked about his sin among men or jinn.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَيَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"Then (on) that Day","translit":"fayawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَّا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يُسْـَٔلُ","english":"will be asked","translit":"yus'alu","root":"سأل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَن","english":"about","translit":"ʿan","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ذَنۢبِهِۦٓ","english":"his sin","translit":"dhanbihi","root":"ذنب"},{"position":6,"arabic":"إِنسٌۭ","english":"any man","translit":"insun","root":"أنس"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"جَآنٌّۭ","english":"any jinn","translit":"jānnun","root":"جنن"}]},{"number":40,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":41,"translation":"The criminals will be known by their marks, and they will be seized by the forelocks and the feet.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يُعْرَفُ","english":"Will be known","translit":"yuʿ'rafu","root":"عرف"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمُجْرِمُونَ","english":"the criminals","translit":"l-muj'rimūna","root":"جرم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِسِيمَـٰهُمْ","english":"by their marks","translit":"bisīmāhum","root":"سوم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَيُؤْخَذُ","english":"and will be seized","translit":"fayu'khadhu","root":"أخذ"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِٱلنَّوَٰصِى","english":"by the forelocks","translit":"bil-nawāṣī","root":"نصي"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَقْدَامِ","english":"and the feet","translit":"wal-aqdāmi","root":"قدم"}]},{"number":42,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":43,"translation":"This is Hell, which the criminals deny.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"هَـٰذِهِۦ","english":"This","translit":"hādhihi","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"جَهَنَّمُ","english":"(is) Hell","translit":"jahannamu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّتِى","english":"which","translit":"allatī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يُكَذِّبُ","english":"deny","translit":"yukadhibu","root":"كذب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِهَا","english":"[of it]","translit":"bihā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْمُجْرِمُونَ","english":"the criminals","translit":"l-muj'rimūna","root":"جرم"}]},{"number":44,"translation":"They will go around between it and scalding water, heated [to the utmost degree].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَطُوفُونَ","english":"They will go around","translit":"yaṭūfūna","root":"طوف"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بَيْنَهَا","english":"between it","translit":"baynahā","root":"بين"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَبَيْنَ","english":"and between","translit":"wabayna","root":"بين"},{"position":4,"arabic":"حَمِيمٍ","english":"scalding water","translit":"ḥamīmin","root":"حمم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ءَانٍۢ","english":"heated","translit":"ānin","root":"أني"}]},{"number":45,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":46,"translation":"But for he who has feared the position of his Lord are two gardens -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلِمَنْ","english":"But for (him) who","translit":"waliman","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"خَافَ","english":"fears","translit":"khāfa","root":"خوف"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَقَامَ","english":"(the) standing","translit":"maqāma","root":"قوم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"رَبِّهِۦ","english":"(before) his Lord","translit":"rabbihi","root":"ربب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"جَنَّتَانِ","english":"(are) two gardens","translit":"jannatāni","root":"جنن"}]},{"number":47,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny? -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":48,"translation":"Having [spreading] branches.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ذَوَاتَآ","english":"Having","translit":"dhawātā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَفْنَانٍۢ","english":"branches","translit":"afnānin","root":"فنن"}]},{"number":49,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":50,"translation":"In both of them are two springs, flowing.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فِيهِمَا","english":"In both of them","translit":"fīhimā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَيْنَانِ","english":"(are) two springs","translit":"ʿaynāni","root":"عين"},{"position":3,"arabic":"تَجْرِيَانِ","english":"flowing","translit":"tajriyāni","root":"جري"}]},{"number":51,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":52,"translation":"In both of them are of every fruit, two kinds.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فِيهِمَا","english":"In both of them","translit":"fīhimā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِن","english":"[of]","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"كُلِّ","english":"(are) every","translit":"kulli","root":"كلل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَـٰكِهَةٍۢ","english":"fruits","translit":"fākihatin","root":"فكه"},{"position":5,"arabic":"زَوْجَانِ","english":"(in) pairs","translit":"zawjāni","root":"زوج"}]},{"number":53,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":54,"translation":"[They are] reclining on beds whose linings are of silk brocade, and the fruit of the two gardens is hanging low.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مُتَّكِـِٔينَ","english":"Reclining","translit":"muttakiīna","root":"وكأ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"on","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"فُرُشٍۭ","english":"couches","translit":"furushin","root":"فرش"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بَطَآئِنُهَا","english":"(whose) inner linings","translit":"baṭāinuhā","root":"بطن"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِنْ","english":"(are) of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"إِسْتَبْرَقٍۢ ۚ","english":"brocade","translit":"is'tabraqin","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَجَنَى","english":"and (the) fruit","translit":"wajanā","root":"جني","audio":"wbw/055_054_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْجَنَّتَيْنِ","english":"(of) both the gardens","translit":"l-janatayni","root":"جنن","audio":"wbw/055_054_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"دَانٍۢ","english":"(is) near","translit":"dānin","root":"دنو","audio":"wbw/055_054_010.mp3"}]},{"number":55,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":56,"translation":"In them are women limiting [their] glances, untouched before them by man or jinni -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فِيهِنَّ","english":"In them","translit":"fīhinna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"قَـٰصِرَٰتُ","english":"(will be) companions of modest gaze","translit":"qāṣirātu","root":"قصر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلطَّرْفِ","english":"(will be) companions of modest gaze","translit":"l-ṭarfi","root":"طرف"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَمْ","english":"not","translit":"lam","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَطْمِثْهُنَّ","english":"has touched them","translit":"yaṭmith'hunna","root":"طمث"},{"position":6,"arabic":"إِنسٌۭ","english":"any man","translit":"insun","root":"أنس"},{"position":7,"arabic":"قَبْلَهُمْ","english":"before them","translit":"qablahum","root":"قبل"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"جَآنٌّۭ","english":"any jinn","translit":"jānnun","root":"جنن"}]},{"number":57,"translation":"So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny? -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"So which","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ءَالَآءِ","english":"(of the) favors","translit":"ālāi","root":"ألو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمَا","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbikumā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبَانِ","english":"will you both deny","translit":"tukadhibāni","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":58,"translation":"As if they were rubies and coral.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَأَنَّهُنَّ","english":"As if they were","translit":"ka-annahunna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْيَاقُوتُ","english":"rubies","translit":"l-yāqūtu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱلْمَرْجَانُ","english":"and coral","translit":"wal-marjānu","